<Base title="Positioning & Messaging" description="A strong positioning framework is your secret weapon for marketing success.">
  <section class="positioning-page">
    <h1>Amplify Your Message</h1>
    <p>Is your software business struggling to communicate a unified message? Are you looking for a way to streamline your marketing efforts and ensure everyone's on the same page? Look no further. A strong positioning framework is your secret weapon for marketing success.</p>

    <h2>Core Components of a Positioning Framework</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Ideal Customer Profile (ICP)</li>
      <li>Ideal Partner Profile (IPP)</li>
      <li>Personas</li>
      <li>Relevant Verticals</li>
      <li>Company Trust: Certifications, Awards, Background and Expertise</li>
      <li>Brand Overview</li>
      <li>Product Name and Category</li>
      <li>Target Customer Segmentation</li>
      <li>Compelling Reasons to Buy</li>
      <li>Competitive Alternatives</li>
      <li>Differentiated Features</li>
      <li>Value Proposition</li>
      <li>Messaging Guidance and Guidelines</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Positioning Services</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>ICP/IPP research and formation</li>
      <li>Persona profiles</li>
      <li>Market research, market gaps and market needs analysis</li>
      <li>Competitive analysis</li>
      <li>Messaging recommendations</li>
      <li>Positioning and messaging documentation</li>
      <li>Positioning and messaging templates</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Express Services</h2>
    <p>Fast. Affordable. On your terms. Ideal for smaller tasks, tight deadlines, or when you just need results, quickly.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>SEO Boost</strong> — Up to 500-word topic pieces focused on your differentiators</li>
      <li><strong>Content for Increased Conversions</strong> — SEO-friendly website pages aligned to your brand voice</li>
      <li><strong>UX Microcopy</strong> — UI content that guides users while reflecting your tone of voice</li>
      <li><strong>Technical and Product Documentation</strong> — User-friendly docs for SaaS, software, and tech products</li>
    </ul>
    <a href="https://www.fiverr.com/rachelcheyfitz" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View on Fiverr</a>
  </section>
</Base>
